{"title":"Proxmox VE使用笔记：在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox VE","date":"2020-06-05T11:24:10.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年6月5日","L":"2020/06/05","MM-DD":"06-05"},"color":"#EBF8FF","link":"articles/bae8ea5c","comments":true,"tags":["Proxmox VE"],"categories":["Proxmox VE使用笔记"],"updated":"2020-06-05T11:32:08.839Z","content":"<h1 id=\"在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox-VE\">在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox VE<a href=\"articles/bae8ea5c#在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox-VE\"></a></h1><p><em>当没有购买订阅时，每次登录Proxmox VE管理界面就会弹出“无有效订阅”窗口。</em></p>\n<p>通过SSH进入Proxmox主机，或通过Web界面访问其控制台，并制作<code>pve-enterprise.list</code>源文件的副本，如下所示:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cp pve-enterprise.list pve-no-subscription.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>打开副本<code>pve-no-subscription.list</code>,原始行如下所示:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deb https://enterprise.proxmox.com/debian/pve stretch pve-enterprise</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>按照如下更改,保存并关闭文件:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deb http://download.proxmox.com/debian/pve stretch pve-no-subscription</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>更新软件包:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>完成后,运行软件升级:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get dist-upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p><strong>主意:</strong> 始终运行<code>apt-get dist-upgrade</code>而不是<code>apt-get upgrade</code></p>\n","next":{"title":"Proxmox VE使用笔记：更换镜像源","link":"articles/10cde004"},"plink":"http://alpac.top/articles/bae8ea5c/","toc":[{"title":"在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox VE","id":"在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox-VE","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Yang Dexuan","link":"<a href=\"http://alpac.top/articles/bae8ea5c/\" title=\"Proxmox VE使用笔记：在不购买订阅的情况下更新Proxmox VE\">http://alpac.top/articles/bae8ea5c/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}